	(3, '2024-05-22 15:22:07', '2024-05-22 15:24:13', 4, '["Maintain Safe Distances: Establish and enforce clear safety zones around overhead electrical lines, ensuring cranes and other equipment stay a safe distance away.","Ensure cranes and other heavy equipment are properly grounded when operating near electrical lines."]', '["Install physical barriers or insulating devices to prevent crane contact with overhead electrical lines.","Implement proximity sensors or alarms on cranes to alert operators when nearing electrical lines."]', '["Explore advancements in crane technology, such as enhanced proximity detection systems or automated collision avoidance features.","Continuously update training programs to incorporate the latest safety practices, equipment operation techniques, and hazard recognition skills"]', '["Azwan could face a temporary or permanent suspension from work, along with being required to undergo additional safety training, and potential legal repercussions based on negligence.","Amir, if responsible for supervising Azwan or ensuring safety protocols, might face similar penalties as Azwan, with potential for demotion or termination depending on severity, and legal consequences if found liable for negligence."]', 1, 1, 1, 1, '/storage/incident-investigation/partb/shosignature/signed_by633729_/signed_by_1716362653.png', '2024-05-22', 5),
